V4 - Real-OS / AIOS feel
  * V4a Wallpaper rebuilt from theme tokens (warm accent bloom + cool deep bloom +
    signal-green wash + diagonal paper gradient) plus a soft vignette; static and
    reduced-motion-safe, adapts across light/dark/midnight themes.
  * V4b New Activity app (default-open) = a clearly-illustrative simulated view of six
